data.description: Stunning Twin Home with 3 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms. This property features a bedroom and full bathroom downstairs. Open Living, Dining and Kitchen area. Kitchen with quartz countertops, wooden cabinets, pantry and stainless steel appliances. Laundry closet on second floor. Extended driveway for multiple car parkings and with one car garage. Fully fenced backyard. Low HOA! Centrally located next to Villages of Homestead, Restaurants, great schools, easy access to the Turnpike and Homestead Air Base and minutes from the Florida Keys. Privacy Fence, full hurricane panels, and the smart home system included.
